1866}

2502static inline void vapi_msg_ip_mfib_details_payload_hton(vapi_payload_ip_mfib_details *payload)
2503{
2504 payload->table_id = htobe32(payload->table_id);
2505 payload->entry_flags = htobe32(payload->entry_flags);
2506 payload->rpf_id = htobe32(payload->rpf_id);
2507 payload->count = htobe32(payload->count);
2508 do { unsigned i; for (i = 0; i < be32toh(payload->count); ++i) { vapi_type_fib_path_hton(&payload->path[i]); } } while(0);
2509}
2510
2511static inline void vapi_msg_ip_mfib_details_payload_ntoh(vapi_payload_ip_mfib_details *payload)
2512{
2513 payload->table_id = be32toh(payload->table_id);
2514 payload->entry_flags = be32toh(payload->entry_flags);
2515 payload->rpf_id = be32toh(payload->rpf_id);
2516 payload->count = be32toh(payload->count);
2517 do { unsigned i; for (i = 0; i < payload->count; ++i) { vapi_type_fib_path_ntoh(&payload->path[i]); } } while(0);
2518}
2519
2520static inline uword vapi_calc_ip_mfib_details_msg_size(vapi_msg_ip_mfib_details *msg)
2521{
2522 return sizeof(*msg)+ msg->payload.count * sizeof(msg->payload.path[0]);

3571 payload->count = htobe32(payload->count);
3572 do { unsigned i; for (i = 0; i < be32toh(payload->count); ++i) { vapi_type_fib_path_hton(&payload->path[i]); } } while(0);
3573}

3580}

3688 vapi_msg_ip_address_dump *msg,

3690 void *callback_ctx,
3691 vapi_error_e rv,
3692 bool is_last,
3693 vapi_payload_ip_address_details *reply),
3694 void *callback_ctx)
3695{

3697 return VAPI_EINVAL;
3698 }
3699 if (vapi_is_nonblocking(ctx) && vapi_requests_full(ctx)) {
3700 return VAPI_EAGAIN;
3701 }
3702 vapi_error_e rv;
3703 if (VAPI_OK != (rv = vapi_producer_lock (ctx))) {
3704 return rv;
3705 }
3706 u32 req_context = vapi_gen_req_context(ctx);
3707 msg->header.context = req_context;
3708 vapi_msg_ip_address_dump_hton(msg);
3709 if (VAPI_OK == (rv = vapi_send_with_control_ping (ctx, msg, req_context))) {
3710 vapi_store_request(ctx, req_context, true, (vapi_cb_t)callback, callback_ctx);
3711 if (VAPI_OK != vapi_producer_unlock (ctx)) {
3712 abort (); /* this really shouldn't happen */
3713 }
3714 if (vapi_is_nonblocking(ctx)) {
3715 rv = VAPI_OK;
3716 } else {
3717 rv = vapi_dispatch(ctx);
3718 }
3719 } else {
3720 vapi_msg_ip_address_dump_ntoh(msg);
3721 if (VAPI_OK != vapi_producer_unlock (ctx)) {
3722 abort (); /* this really shouldn't happen */
3723 }
3724 }
3725 return rv;
3726}
